title: Brawlhalla X SpongeBob SquarePants - Official Crossover Reveal Trailer
description:
Brawlhalla is a 2D free-to-play platform brawler fighting game developed by Ubisoft. Brawlhalla has just announced a new collaboration with the hit Nickelodeon series SpongeBob SquarePants where players will be able to fight as SpongeBob, Sandy, and Patrick. The Brawhalla X SpongeBob SquarePants Crossover Event starts on November 29 for PlayStation 4, Xbox One, Xbox Series S|X, Nintendo Switch, macOS, Mobile, and PC.

#Brawlhalla #SpongeBobSquarePants

title: Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 Single-Player Campaign Review
description:
Underbaked, rehashed, and cobbled together from multiplayer parts, Modern Warfare 3’s single-player campaign is everything a Call of Duty story mode shouldn’t be. Check out our full written review here.

Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 is released 10th November on PS4, PS5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X/S, and PC.
